* The Face of Apartheid<ref name="Crowther1971">{{cite book|author=Clarence Edward Crowther|title=The Face of Apartheid|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=SwqQAAAACAAJ|accessdate=16 September 2013|date=1 January 1971|publisher=New Zealand University Press|isbn=978-0-7055-0341-9}}</ref>
