'''Party of Labour Basel (founded in 1944)''' (in [[German language|German]]: ''Partei der Arbeit Basel (gegr. 1944)''), a splinter group of [[Swiss Party of Labour]] in [[Basel]]. PdA 1944 was formed in 1988. It is somewhat more orthodox than the main PdA.

