'''President of the Municipal Chamber''', or ''Presidente da Câmara Municipal'', in [[Portuguese language|Portuguese]], is the title of the [[Mayor]], in [[Portugal]] and other Portuguese speaking countries. In [[Brazil]], the title is "Prefect", or ''Prefeito''.

